name: MARE MAGNVM: VLTRAMARINI by Edison Peñafiel

metadata.name: MARE MAGNVM: VLTRAMARINI XIV
metadata.description: A prequel and sequel, a link to the MARE MAGNVM series that centers on real-life scenes from the many migration episodes across bodies of water around the globe, the MARE MAGNVM: VLTRAMARINI XIV exhibits the precise moment when those beyond the sea finally arrive at an unidentified coastline.
